articles.author: Foo Yun Chee
articles.title: No more chicken Big Macs - EU court rules against McDonald's in trademark case - Reuters
articles.description: U.S. fast-food chain McDonald's does not have the right to use the term "Big Mac" for poultry products after it had not used it for them for five consecutive years, Europe's second top court said on Wednesday, in a partial win for Irish rival Supermac's in a …
